        </h1>
        <p>Selling some old vinyl. All records at <b>Helsinki</b>. <a href="mailto:jaywink@basshero.org">Email</a>, SMS or call me (+358451259376). Buy many and get a massive discount. Will post at buyers expense for orders of more than 5.</p><p>Condition: VG - Very Good, G - Good, F - Fair, P - Poor</p>
